cs.DC, cs.PF, cs.AR, cs.SE, cs.SY 

The paper discusses the optimization of parallel application execution in heterogeneous HPC systems, which involves topics related to distributed computing (cs.DC), performance analysis and optimization (cs.PF), architecture (cs.AR), software engineering (cs.SE), and systems and control (cs.SY). The focus on power consumption also suggests a potential fit with the cs.AR sub-category.
